ords of user and admin events in this realm. To configure the tracking of these events, go to <1>Event configs</1>.\"},{\"key\":\"permit\",\"value\":\"Permit\"},{\"key\":\"effectiveMessageBundlesHelp\",\"value\":\"You can search for effective message bundles based on themes, features, language, and free text.\"},{\"key\":\"eventTypes.LOGOUT.description\",\"value\":\"Logout\"},{\"key\":\"customValue\",\"value\":\"Custom value\"},{\"key\":\"overrideActionTokensHelp\",\"value\":\"Override default settings of maximum time before an action permit sent by a user (such as a forgot password e-mail) is expired for specific action. This value is recommended to be short because it's expected that the user would react to self-created action quickly.\"},{\"key\":\"searchByName\",\"value\":\"Search by name\"},{\"key\":\"attributeConsumingServiceNameHelp\",\"value\":\"Name of the Attribute Consuming Service profile to advertise in the SP metadata.\"},{\"key\":\"used.SPECIFIC_CLIENTS\",\"value\":\"Specific clients\"},{\"key\":\"freeMemory\",\"value\":\"Free memory\"},{\"key\":\"applyPolicy\",\"value\":\"Apply policy\"},{\"key\":\"directGrantHelp\",\"value\":\"Select the flow you want to use for direct grant authentication.\"},{\"key\":\"unlockUsersSuccess\",\"value\":\"Any temporarily locked users are now unlocked\"},{\"key\":\"enableStartTLS\",\"value\":\"Enable StartTLS\"},{\"key\":\"syncModeOverride\",\"value\":\"Sync mode override\"},{\"key\":\"inviteSent\",\"value\":\"Invitation has been sent.\"},{\"key\":\"conditionsHelpItem\",\"value\":\"Conditions help item\"},{\"key\":\"clientPoliciesPoliciesHelpText\",\"value\":\"Client Policy allows to bind client profiles with various conditions to specify when exactly is enforced behavior specified by executors of the particular client profile.\"},{\"key\":\"usermodel.attr.label\",\"value\":\"User Attribute\"},{\"key\":\"eventTypes.REGISTER.name\",\"value\":\"Register\"},{\"key\":\"webAuthnPolicyUserVerificationRequirementHelp\",\"valu