d or assigned in advance to the client to determine whether the policy is applied to this client. Condition is evaluated during OpenID Connect authorization request and/or token request.\"},{\"key\":\"bruteForceMode.PermanentLockout\",\"value\":\"Lockout permanently\"},{\"key\":\"mappingUpdatedSuccess\",\"value\":\"Mapping successfully updated\"},{\"key\":\"logoUrlHelp\",\"value\":\"URL that references a logo for the Client application\"},{\"key\":\"searchClientAuthorizationResource\",\"value\":\"Search resource\"},{\"key\":\"clientTypeHelp\",\"value\":\"'OpenID Connect' allows Clients to verify the identity of the End-User based on the authentication performed by an Authorization Server.'SAML' enables web-based authentication and authorization scenarios including cross-domain single sign-on (SSO) and uses security tokens containing assertions to pass information.\"},{\"key\":\"searchClientByName\",\"value\":\"Search client by name\"},{\"key\":\"loginTimeout\",\"value\":\"Login timeout\"},{\"key\":\"updateError\",\"value\":\"Could not update the provider {{error}}\"},{\"key\":\"emptyClientProfilesInstructions\",\"value\":\"There are no profiles, select 'Create client profile' to create a new client profile\"},{\"key\":\"manage\",\"value\":\"Manage\"},{\"key\":\"searchForSession\",\"value\":\"Search session\"},{\"key\":\"noSessionsDescription\",\"value\":\"There are currently no active sessions in this realm.\"},{\"key\":\"sendIdTokenOnLogout\",\"value\":\"Send 'id_token_hint' in logout requests\"},{\"key\":\"authenticatorRefConfig.maxAge.label\",\"value\":\"Authenticator Reference Max Age\"},{\"key\":\"createGroupText\",\"value\":\"Create attributes group\"},{\"key\":\"disableSigningExplain\",\"value\":\"If you disable \\\"{{key}}\\\", the Keycloak database will be updated and you may need to download a new adapter for this client.\"},{\"key\":\"mapperTypeRoleLdapMapperHelp\",\"value\":\"Used to map role mappings of roles from some LDAP DN to Keycloak role mappings 