ient session is expired. Tokens are invalidated when a session is expired. The option does not affect the global user SSO session. If not set, it uses the standard SSO Session Max value.\"},{\"key\":\"storePasswordHelp\",\"value\":\"Password to access the archive itself\"},{\"key\":\"showPassword\",\"value\":\"Show password field in clear text\"},{\"key\":\"scopePermissions.groups.manage-membership-description\",\"value\":\"Policies that decide if an administrator can add or remove users from this group\"},{\"key\":\"resourceType\",\"value\":\"Resource type\"},{\"key\":\"selectUserInfoSignedResponseAlgorithm\",\"value\":\"Select user info signed response algorithm\"},{\"key\":\"eventTypes.CODE_TO_TOKEN.name\",\"value\":\"Code to token\"},{\"key\":\"mode\",\"value\":\"Mode\"},{\"key\":\"kc.realm.name\",\"value\":\"Realm\"},{\"key\":\"mappingTable\",\"value\":\"Table with predefined mapping\"},{\"key\":\"always\",\"value\":\"Always\"},{\"key\":\"pkceEnabledHelp\",\"value\":\"Use PKCE (Proof of Key-code exchange) for IdP Brokering\"},{\"key\":\"disableConfirmClientTitle\",\"value\":\"Disable client?\"},{\"key\":\"noNodes\",\"value\":\"No nodes registered\"},{\"key\":\"useTruststoreSpi\",\"value\":\"Use Truststore SPI\"},{\"key\":\"showDataBtn\",\"value\":\"Show data\"},{\"key\":\"dedicatedScopeDescription\",\"value\":\"Dedicated scope and mappers for this client\"},{\"key\":\"updatePasswordPolicySuccess\",\"value\":\"Password policies successfully updated\"},{\"key\":\"clientsExplain\",\"value\":\"Clients are applications and services that can request authentication of a user.\"},{\"key\":\"policy-description\",\"value\":\"A description for this policy.\"},{\"key\":\"used.SPECIFIC_PROVIDERS\",\"value\":\"Specific providers\"},{\"key\":\"scopePermissions.groups.view-description\",\"value\":\"Policies that decide if an administrator can view this group\"},{\"key\":\"encryptAssertionsHelp\",\"value\":\"Should SAML assertions be encrypted with client's public key using AES